0Republic%20Day%20preparations%20and%20celebrations.%20The%20restrictions%2C%20outlined%20in%20a%20Notice%20to%20Airmen%20(NOTAM)%2C%20apply%20to%20both%20arrivals%20and%20departures%20and%20affect%20all%20types%20of%20flights%2C%20including%20non-scheduled%2C%20scheduled%2C%20and%20chartered%20flights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PTI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20group%20of%20billionaires%20and%20millionaires%20have%20called%20on%20world%20leaders%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20to%20fight%20social%20inequality%20by%20taxing%20the%20rich.%20But%20there%20is%20political%20resistance.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20surprised%20that%20you%20have%20failed%20to%20answer%20a%20simple%20question%20that%20we%20have%20been%20asking%20for%20three%20years%3A%20when%20will%20you%20tax%20extreme%20wealth%3F%E2%80%9D%20begins%20the%20open%20letter%20by%20an%20initiative%20called%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fproudtopaymore.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EProud%20to%20Pay%20More%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Directed%20at%20%E2%80%9Cglobal%20leaders%20gathering%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-economic-forum%2Ft-39621193%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDavos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20world%20leaders%20gathered%20at%20the%20Swiss%20ski%20resort%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20signatories%20are%20demanding%20higher%20taxes%20be%20levied%20on%20the%20super-rich.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20many%20of%20the%20signatories%20are%20among%20the%20wealthiest%20people%20in%20the%20world.%20Proud%20to%20Pay%20More%20comprises%20at%20least%20260%20billionaires%20and%20millionaires%20who%20say%20that%20steps%20must%20be%20taken%20%E2%80%9Cto%20address%20the%20dramatic%20rise%20of%20social%20inequality.%E2%80%9D%20They%20say%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctipping%20point%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20reached%2C%20whose%20%E2%80%9Ccost%20to%20our%20economic%2C%20societal%2C%20and%20ecological%20stability%20risk%20is%20severe%20%E2%80%94%20and%20growing%20every%20day.%20In%20short%2C%20we%20need%20action%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20their%20drive%20for%20fairer%20taxes%20represents%C2%A0%E2%80%9Ca%20return%20to%20normality%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20arguing%20that%20taxing%20the%20rich%20will%20%E2%80%9Cturn%20extreme%20and%20unproductive%20private%20wealth%20into%20an%20investment%20for%20our%20common%20democratic%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98We%20believe%20we%20must%20be%20taxed%20more%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20moment%20of%20delay%20entrenches%20the%20dangerous%20economic%20status%20quo%2C%20threatens%20our%20democratic%20norms%2C%20and%20passes%20the%20buck%20to%20our%20children%20and%20grandchildren%2C%E2%80%9D%20write%20the%20signatories%2C%20who%20include%20heiresses%20Valerie%20Rockefeller%2C%20Abigail%20Disney%20and%20Marlene%20Engelhorn%2C%20an%20Austrian%20national%20whose%20forefather%20Friedrich%20Engelhorn%20founded%20German%20chemicals%20company%20BASF.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20do%20we%20want%20to%20be%20taxed%20more%20but%20we%20believe%20we%20must%20be%20taxed%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngelhorn%2C%20who%20has%20criticized%20the%20fact%20that%20Austria%20does%20not%20have%20an%20inheritance%20tax%2C%20recently%20made%20the%20headlines%20when%20she%20said%20she%20wanted%20to%20redistribute%20%E2%82%AC25%20million%20(%2427%20million)%20of%20her%20inherited%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20inherited%20a%20fortune%2C%20and%20therefore%20power%2C%20without%20having%20done%20anything%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20reporters.%20She%20has%20set%20up%20a%20Good%20Council%20for%20Redistribution%20to%20develop%20solutions%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinterest%20of%20society%20as%20a%20whole.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rich%20get%20richer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20richer%20and%20richer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcan-a-wealth-tax-bridge-germanys-divide-between-rich-and-poor%2Fa-50185609%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Egap%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0continues%20to%20widen%20worldwide.%20According%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwir2022.wid.world%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorld%20Inequality%20Report%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%2038%25%20of%20the%20global%20increment%20in%20wealth%20between%201995%20and%202021%20went%20to%20the%20top%201%25.%20Only%202%25%20went%20to%20the%20bottom%20half%2C%20namely%20the%204%20billion%20poorest%20people%20in%20the%20world.%20And%20after%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%20in%202020%2C%20global%20billionaire%20wealth%20rose%20more%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20world%2C%20there%20have%20already%20been%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbiden-budget-plan-proposes-higher-taxes-on-the-rich%2Fa-61270998%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eseveral%20attempts%20to%20tax%20large%20fortunes%20more.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0For%20example%2C%20in%20the%202019%20presidential%20campaign%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Senator%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20proposed%20an%20%E2%80%9Cultra-millionaire%20tax%E2%80%9D%20on%20every%20dollar%20of%20net%20worth%20above%20%2450%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20easy%20to%20implement%20such%20measures.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20signatories%20of%20the%20petition%20in%20Davos%20are%20mainly%20heirs%20who%20do%20not%20actively%20run%20a%20company%2C%20and%20therefore%20feel%20uncomfortable%20with%20great%20wealth%20that%20they%20have%20not%20generated%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20explained%20Stefan%20Bach%20from%20the%20German%20Institute%20for%20Economic%20Research%20(DIW)%20in%20Berlin.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20isolated%20voices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2