%20taken%20from%20a%20business-class%20seat%2C%20accompanied%20the%20post%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20The%20in-flight%20entertainment%20screen%20in%20the%20photo%20shows%20a%20route%20map%20from%20Miami%20to%20Munich%2C%20and%20a%20Macbook%20screen%20%E2%80%94%20alongside%20a%20coffee%20and%20glass%20of%20water%20%E2%80%94%20that%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BJournal%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Munich.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post%2C%20Bush%20shared%20several%20suggestions%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravelers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20traveling%20with%20only%20carry-on%20bags%2C%20stretching%20before%20getting%20on%20board%2C%20listening%20to%20albums%20and%20podcasts%20on%20Spotify%2C%20and%20keeping%20an%20%26quot%3Bairplane%20journal%26quot%3B%20on%20your%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOne%20piece%20of%20advice%20drew%20people's%20attention.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoard%20in%20Group%201%2C%20no%20matter%20your%20group.%2099%25%20of%20the%20time%20they%20don't%20say%20anything.%20Worst%20case%20they%20tell%20you%20to%20wait%2C%20then%20you're%20first%20when%20they%20call%20your%20actual%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20Bush%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBush's%20LinkedIn%20post%20garnered%20508%20reactions%20and%20229%20comments%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing.%20But%20Bush's%20advice%20gained%20more%20traction%20on%20Reddit%2C%20where%20a%20screenshot%20of%20his%20LinkedIn%20post%20was%20uploaded.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fdelta%2Fcomments%2F194ffqg%2Fsaw_this_advice_and_comments_on_linkedin_these%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReddit%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20garnered%204%2C200%20upvotes%20and%20674%20comments%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSaw%20this%20%26quot%3Badvice%26quot%3B%20and%20comments%20on%20LinkedIn%20-%20these%20are%20the%20scumbags%20who%20ruin%20things%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20where%20several%20people%20agreed%20with%20his%20suggestion%2C%20on%20Reddit%2C%20there%20was%20more%20criticism%20of%20Bush's%20suggestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20noted%20that%20Bush%20fit%20the%20description%20of%20%26quot%3Bgate%20lice%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20unflattering%20nickname%20flight%20attendants%20use%20for%20people%20who%20rush%20to%20board%20first%20so%20they%20can%20secure%20overhead%20space%20%E2%80%94%20or%20cut%20the%20line%20before%20their%20turn%20is%20called.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20should%20be%20a%20wraparound%20lane%20you%20have%20to%20exit%20thru%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20line%20if%20you%20try%20this.%20I%20wish%20they%20would%20ask%20me%20to%20design%20the%20entry%20to%20the%20planes%E2%80%A6I%20would%20set%20it%20up%20to%20make%20gate%20lice%20obsolete%20and%20punish%20these%20fraudulent%20entitled%20early%20boarder%20attempts%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%20commented%3A%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20who%20does%20this%20is%20the%20worst%20type%20of%20person.%20If%20you%20do%20this%20it's%20similar%20to%20parking%20in%20a%20handicap%20spot%20it's%20that%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20travelers%20have%20shared%20controversial%20opinions%20on%20flying%20online.%20In%20December%2C%20people%20online%20criticized%20a%20mom%20for%20being%20wasteful%20after%20sharing%20that%20she%20uses%20painter's%20tape%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-flights-kids-mom-flight-attendant-tips-painters-tape-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentertain%20her%20kids%20on%20flights%20on%20TikTok.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20January%2C%20a%20former%20flight%20attendant%20shared%20in%20an%20online%20podcast%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foverhead-bin-space-not-guaranteed-to-passengers-flying-economy-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomy%20passengers%20aren't%20