0possible%2C%20which%20have%20led%20to%20increased%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forumdisuguaglianzediversita.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2FSocial-Media-Political-Polarization-and-Political-Disinformation-Literature-Review.x28591.pdf%5C%22%3Epolitical%20polarisation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20global%20populism%20and%20an%20epidemic%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS1054139X20301075%5C%22%3Eonline%20harassment%20and%20bullying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20all%20this%2C%20free%20speech%20has%20become%20a%20totemic%20issue%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2Fj.ctv199td7w%5C%22%3Ethe%20culture%20wars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20its%20status%20both%20boosted%20and%20threatened%20by%20the%20societal%20forces%20unleashed%20by%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20free%20speech%20debates%20tend%20to%20be%20caught%20up%20with%20arguments%20about%20%E2%80%9Ccancel%20culture%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwoke%E2%80%9D%20mindset.%20This%20risks%20overlooking%20the%20impact%20technology%20is%20having%20on%20how%20freedom%20of%20expression%20laws%20actually%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20the%20way%20that%20AI%20gives%20governments%20and%20tech%20companies%20the%20ability%20to%20censor%20expression%20with%20increasing%20ease%2C%20and%20at%20great%20scale%20and%20speed.%20This%20is%20a%20serious%20issue%20that%20I%20explore%20in%20my%20new%20book%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomsbury.com%2Fuk%2Ffuture-of-language-9781350278851%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Future%20of%20Language%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20delicate%20balance%20of%20free%20speech%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20most%20important%20protections%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coe.int%2Fen%2Fweb%2Fhuman-rights-convention%2Fexpression%5C%22%3Efree%20speech%20in%20liberal%20democracies%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20US%20rely%20on%20technicalities%20in%20how%20the%20law%20responds%20to%20the%20real-life%20actions%20of%20everyday%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20element%20of%20the%20current%20system%20relies%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20we%2C%20as%20autonomous%20individuals%2C%20have%20the%20unique%20ability%20to%20transform%20our%20ideas%20into%20words%20and%20communicate%20these%20to%20others.%20This%20may%20seem%20a%20rather%20unremarkable%20point.%20But%20the%20way%20the%20law%20currently%20works%20is%20based%20on%20this%20simple%20assumption%20about%20human%20social%20behaviour%2C%20and%20it's%20something%20that%20AI%20threatens%20to%20undermine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFree%20speech%20protections%20in%20many%20liberal%20societies%20rule%20against%20the%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdictionary.law.com%2FDefault.aspx%3Fselected%3D1606%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cprior%20restraint%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%2C%20blocking%20an%20utterance%20before%20it's%20been%20expressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20should%20not%20be%20able%20to%20prevent%20a%20newspaper%20from%20publishing%20a%20particular%20story%2C%20although%20it%20can%20prosecute%20it%20for%20doing%20so%20after%20publication%20if%20it%20thinks%20the%20story%20is%20breaking%20any%20laws.%20The%20use%20of%20prior%20restraint%20is%20already%20widespread%20in%20countries%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cecc.gov%2Fprior-restraints%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20have%20very%20different%20attitudes%20to%20the%20regulation%20of%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20significant%20because%2C%20despite%20what%20tech%20libertarians%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2022%2Fapr%2F14%2Fhow-free-speech-absolutist-elon-musk-would-transform-twitter%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20may%20assert%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20no%20society%20in%20the%20world%20allows%20for%20absolute%20freedom%20of%20speech.%20There's%20always%20a%20balance%20to%20be%20struck%20between%20protecting%20people%20from%20the%20real%20harm%20that%20language%20can%20cause%20(for%20example%20by%20defaming%20them)%2C%20and%20safeguarding%20people's%20right%20to%20express%20conflicting%20opinions%20and%20criticise%20those%20in%20power.%20Finding%20the%20right%20balance%20between%20these%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20decisions%20a%20society%20is%20faced%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EAI%20and%20prior%20restraint%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20so%20much%20of%20our%20communication%20today%20is%20mediated%20by%20technology%2C%20it%20is%20now%20extremely%20easy%20for%20AI%20assistance%20to%20be%20used%20to%20enact%20prior%20restraint%2C%20and%20to%20do%20so%20at%20great%20speed%20and%20massive%20scale.%20This%20would%20create%20circumstances%20in%20which%20that%20basic%20human%20ability%20to%20turn%20ideas%20into%20speech%20could%20be%20compromised%2C%20as%20and%20when%20a%20government%20(or%20social%20media%20exec)%20wishes%20it%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legislation.gov.uk%2Fukpga%2F2023%2F50%2Fenacted%5C%22%3EOnline%20Safety%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20as%20well%20plans%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20to%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liberties.eu%2Fen%2Fstories%2Fuploa-filter-back-eu-2020%2F18938%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cupload%20filtering%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20(algorithmic%20tools%20for%20blocking%20certain%20content%20from%20being%20uploaded)%20as%20a%20way%20of%20screening%20for%20offensive%20or%20illegal%20posts%2C%20all%20encourage%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20censor%20at%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rationale%20given%20for%20this%20is%20a%20practical%20one.%20With%20such%20a%20huge%20quantity%20of%20content%20being%20uploaded%20every%20minute%20of%20every%20day%2C%20it%20becomes%20extremely%20challenging%20for%20teams%20of%20humans%20to%20monitor%20everything.%20AI%20is%20a%20fast%20and%20far%20less%20expensive%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20also%20automated%2C%20unable%20to%20bring%20real-life%20experience%20to%20bear%2C%20and%20its%20decisions%20are%20rarely%20subject%20to%20public%20scrutiny.%20The%20consequences%20of%20this%20are%20that%20AI-driven%20filters%20can%20often%20lean%20towards%20censoring%20content%20which%20is%20neither%20illegal%20or%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFree%20speech%20as%20we%20understand%20it%20today%20relies%20on%20specific%20legal%20processes%20of%20protection%20that%20have%20developed%20over%20centuries.%20It's%20not%20an%20abstract%20idea%2C%20but%20one%20grounded%20in%20very%20particular%20social%20and%20legal%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegislation%20that%20encourages%20content%20regulation%20by%20automation%20effectively%20dismisses%20these%20processes%20as%20technicalities.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20risks%20jeopardising%20the%20entire%20institution%20of%20free%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFree%20speech%20will%20always%20be%20an%20idea%20sustained%20by%20ongoing%20debate.%20There's%20never%20a%20settled%20formula%20for%20defining%20what%20should%20be%20outlawed%20and%20what%20not.%20This%20is%20why%20determining%20what%20counts%20as%20acceptable%20and%20unacceptable%20needs%20to%20take%20place%20in%20open%20society%20and%20be%20subject%20to%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20indications%20that%20some%20governments%20are%20beginning%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opensocietyfoundations.org%2Fnewsroom%2Fopen-society-and-other-funders-launch-new-initiative-to-ensure-ai-advances-the-public-interest%5C%22%3Eacknowledge%20this%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20planning%20for%20the%20future%20of%20AI%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20centre%20stage%20in%20all%20such%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20role%20AI%20may%20play%20in%20helping%20to%20monitor%20online%20content%2C%20it%20mustn't%20constrain%20our%20ability%20to%20argue%20among%20ourselves%20about%20what%20sort%20of