ut%20who%20had%20challenged%20the%20very%20basis%20of%20the%20American%20democratic%20order.%20He%20is%20once%20again%20making%20a%20case%20to%20Americans%20that%20among%20the%20political%20class%2C%20he%20is%20still%20best%20suited%20to%20take%20the%20oath%20of%20protecting%20the%20American%20Constitution.%20And%20much%20to%20the%20astonishment%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20many%20in%20the%20US%20are%20willing%20to%20buy%20his%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20achieved%20a%20historic%20win%20at%20the%20Iowa%20Republican%20caucuses%20earlier%20this%20week%20in%20the%20first%20contest%20in%20the%20race%20for%20a%20presidential%20nominee.%20It%20was%20landslide%20as%20he%20won%20the%20most%20votes%20in%20all%20but%20one%20of%20Iowa's%2099%20counties%20and%20he%20won%20across%20all%20segments%20of%20the%20voters%20-%20men%20and%20women%2C%20the%20young%20and%20old%2C%20the%20evangelical%20and%20hard-right%20conservative%2C%20even%20college-educated%20Republicans.%20Trump's%20opponents%20have%20a%20difficult%20road%20ahead.%20Though%20Nikki%20Haley%20is%20slated%20to%20do%20better%20in%20a%20relatively%20moderate%20New%20Hampshire%20next%20week%20as%20there%20has%20been%20a%20surge%20in%20her%20polling%20numbers%20and%20funding%2C%20she%20will%20have%20to%20put%20up%20a%20really%20strong%20performance%20to%20make%20a%20dent%20in%20Trump's%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Trump%20views%20Haley%20as%20the%20only%20real%20challenger%20left%20in%20the%20race%20now%20is%20evidenced%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20is%20now%20targeting%20her%20origins.%20He%20referred%20to%20her%20by%20her%20first%20name%2C%20Nimarata%2C%20and%20has%20resorted%20to%20a%20misinformation%20campaign%20by%20supporting%20rumors%20she%20was%20ineligible%20to%20run%20for%20president%20because%20her%20parents%20were%20not%20US%20citizens%20at%20the%20time%20of%20her%20birth.%20For%20Haley%20it%20is%20a%20difficult%20balancing%20act.%20She%20has%20to%20attack%20Trump%20and%20his%20record%20but%20also%20ensure%20that%20his%20support%20base%20does%20not%20get%20completely%20alienated.%20So%2C%20while%20she%20has%20targeted%20Trump%20and%20Biden%20by%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Byou%20don't%20defeat%20Democratic%20chaos%20with%20Republican%20chaos%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20also%20largely%20maintained%20a%20distance%20from%20commenting%20on%20the%20numerous%20court%20cases%20Trump%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20managed%20to%20convince%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20Republican%20base%20that%20he%20never%20lost%20the%202020%20presidential%20elections.%20And%20the%20more%20he%20has%20been%20dragged%20to%20the%20courts%2C%20the%20more%20his%20popularity%20has%20gone%20up%20among%20his%20base%2C%20which%20believes%20that%20he%20is%20being%20targeted%20for%20political%20reasons.%20He%20is%20redefining%20the%20standard%20political%20trajectories%20of%20former%20presidents%20and%20presidential%20hopefuls.%20A%20defeated%20presidential%20candidate%20tends%20to%20gradually%20disappear%20from%20public%20presence.%20But%20here%20is%20a%20former%20president%20who%20lost%20to%20his%20political%20opponent%20three%20years%20ago%20and%20then%20supported%20the%20January%206%20capitol%20riots%20while%20not%20conceding%20his%20defeat.%20Trump%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20ballot%20in%20Maine%20and%20Colorado%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20now%20in%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20will%20begin%20to%20hear%20arguments%20from%20next%20month.%20Yet%20he%20has%20already%20made%20a%20remarkable%20political%20comeback%20in%20Iowa%2C%20as%20if%20his%20is%20a%20clean%20slate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20the%20Republican%20Party%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20over%20Trump%20but%20as%20his%20massive%20win%20in%20Iowa%20has%20shown%2C%20he%20remains%20the%20undisputed%20leader%20of%20the%20party.%20Today's%20GOP%20has%20been%20reconstituted%20in%20Trump's%20image%20and%20there%20is%20very%20little%20his%20opponents%20have%20been%20able%20to%20do%20about%20it.%20Trump's%20supporters%20have%20effective%20control%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party%20at%20all%20levels%20across%20the%20country%2C%20thereby%20giving%20him%20a%20significant%20advantage%20over%20his%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20now%20seems%20very%20likely%20that%20despite%20the%20best%20efforts%20of%20his%20rivals%2C%20Trump%20will%20be%20on%20the%20Republican%20ticket%20challenging%20the%20Democratic%20incumbent.%20It%20will%20then%20be%20a%20handful%20of%20swing%20states%20that%20will%20decide%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20Presidential%20race%20where%20recent%20polls%20have%20shown%20Trump%20to%20be%20highly%20competitive.%20A%20close%20election%20is%20on%20the%20cards%20with%20the%20likelihood%20that%20polarization%20in%20America%20is%20going%20to%20become%20even%20more%20entrenched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerican%20presidential%20elections%20matter%20not%20only%20for%20Americans%20but%20also%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20Trump's%20comeback%20is%20being%20watched%20carefully%20in%20world%20capitals%2C%20from%20Moscow%20and%20Beijing%20to%20Brussels%20and%20New%20Delhi.%20What%20is%20also%20being%20watched%20is%20the%20fraying%20of%20the%20American%20institutional%20fabric.%20A%20nation%20that%20has%20always%20been%20keen%20to%20lecture%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20on%20democratic%20credentials%2C%20today%20finds%20itself%20in%20an%20unenviable%20position%20of%20accommodating%20the%20resurrection%20of%20a%20leader%20who%20challenged%20the%20very%20foundations%20of%20American%20democracy%20three%20years%20ago%20when%20he%20told%20a%20mob%20to%20%26quot%3Bfight%20like%20hell%26quot%3B%20before%20it%20ransacked%20the%20US%20Capitol%20to%20deny%20Joe%20Biden%20his%202020%20election%20win.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20world%20engages%20with%20another%20year%20of%20the%20American%20democratic%20spectacle%2C%20it%20bears%20reminding%20that%20democracy%20is%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20centrestage%20of%20American%20politics%20shows%20that%20the%20self-proclaimed%20beacon%20of%20democracy%20faces%20challenging%20times%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Harsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20book%20is%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20Afghan%20Muddle%26quot%3B%20(HarperCollins))%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705652160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fqhmaj1g_us-election-generic_625x300_28_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-dystopia-that-is-american-democracy-today-4891752%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world%20is%20passing%20through%20a%20phase%20of%20disorder%2C%20which%20is%20posing%20serious%20policy%20questions%20for%20nations%20big%20and%20small.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-dystopia-that-is-american-democracy-today-4891752%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-dystopia-that-is-american-democracy-today-4891752%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-dystopia-that-is-american-democracy-today-4891752%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aadhaar%20Card%20No%20Longer%20Acceptable%20as%20Proof%20of%20Date%20of%20Birth%3A%20EPFO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F09105721%2FAadhaar.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Employees%E2%80%99%20Provident%20Fund%20Organisation%20(EPFO)%20will%20no%20longer%20accept%20Aadhaar%20Card%20as%20proof%20of%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20the%20retirement%20fund%20body%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20(January%2016).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%