%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20has%20the%20secretaries%20of%20the%20Union%20ministries%20of%20Home%2C%20Law%2C%20Tribal%20Affairs%2C%20and%20Social%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20no%20deadline%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20before%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20Telangana%20last%20year%2C%20reports%20had%20claimed%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20set%20the%20ball%20rolling%20to%20establish%20a%C2%A0%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20the%20Madiga%20community.%20The%20Madigas%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705651232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fcase-in-apex-court-union-govt-forms-panel-for-equitable-distribution-of-benefits-among-sc-groups%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20seven-judge%20constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20parallely%20consider%20whether%20sub-categorisation%20of%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20communities%20is%20permissible.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fcase-in-apex-court-union-govt-forms-panel-for-equitable-distribution-of-benefits-among-sc-groups%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Priyanka-%20Nick%20visit%20Malibu%20Hindu%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705651214000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106982257%2Cimgsize-114142.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopra-and-nick-jonas-malibu-hindu-temple-visit-on-malti-maries-birthday%2Farticleshow%2F106982257.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106982257.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPriyanka%20Chopra%20and%20Nick%20Jonas%20have%20warmly%20embraced%20parenthood%2C%20celebrating%20the%20second%20birthday%20of%20their%20daughter%2C%20Malti%20Marie%20Chopra%20Jonas%2C%20born%20via%20surrogacy%20on%20January%2015.%20The%20family%20marked%20the%20occasion%20by%20visiting%20the%20Malibu%20Hindu%20Temple%2C%20seeking%20blessings%2C%20with%20a%20fan%20capturing%20the%20down-to-earth%20couple%20during%20the%20visit.%20Malti's%20birthday%20festivities%20continued%2C%20as%20Priyanka%20shared%20charming%20glimpses%20on%20Instagram.%20The%20initial%20photo%20showcased%20Malti%20in%20a%20white%20dress%20with%20a%20large%20garland%2C%20her%20adorable%20charm%20accentuated%20by%20a%20green%20bindi.%20Priyanka%20affectionately%20referred%20to%20Malti%20as%20their%20miracle%2C%20now%20turning%20two.%20Nick%20Jonas%20also%20joined%20in%2C%20sharing%20pictures%20from%20the%20celebration%20and%20humorously%20expressing%20uncertainty%20about%20disciplining%20Malti.%20Priyanka's%20recent%20works%20include%20the%20romantic%20comedy%20'Love%20Again'%20and%20the%20spy%20thriller%20series%20Citadel.%20Her%20upcoming%20project%2C%20'Heads%20of%20State%2C'%20directed%20by%20Ilya%20Naishuller%2C%20features%20an%20impressive%20cast%2C%20including%20Idris%20Elba%20and%20John%20Cena.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopra-and-nick-jonas-malibu-hindu-temple-visit-on-malti-maries-birthday%2Farticleshow%2F106982257.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thailand's%20Ayutthaya%2C%20India's%20Ayodhya%3A%20Divided%20By%20Borders%2C%20United%20By%20Faith%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAyodhya%20and%20Ayutthaya%2C%20one%20in%20India%20and%20the%20other%20in%20Thailand.%20Separated%20by%20geographical%20boundaries%2C%20the%20two%20towns%20are%20united%20not%20just%20in%20name%20but%20also%20in%20faith%20with%20the%20religious%20fervour%20in%20the%20home%20of%20Ram%20finding%20echo%203%2C500%20km%20away%20in%20a%20foreign%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ayodhya%20gets%20ready%20for%20the%20consecration%20of%20a%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20three%20days%20away%2C%20devotees%20in%20Ayutthaya%20are%20also%20preparing%20to%20join%20the%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ayodhya%20temple%20trust%20has%20also%20received%20soil%20from%20Ayutthaya%20--%20named%20after%20Ayodhya%20--%20and%20water%20from%20Thailand's%20three%20rivers%2C%20including%20Chao%20Phraya%2C%20Lop%20Buri%20and%20Pa%20Sak%20for%20the%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENestled%20along%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Chao%20Phraya%20River%2C%20the%20ancient%20city%20of%20Ayutthaya%20is%20located%2070%20km%20north%20of%20Bangkok%20and%20features%20on%20the%20list%20of%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20sites%20for%20its%20rich%20and%20vibrant%20cultural%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20member%20from%20Bangkok%2C%20huge%20screens%20are%20being%20put%20up%20in%20Hindu%20temples%20in%20Ayutthaya%20and%20other%20cities%20in%20Thailand%20for%20the%20live%20telecast%20of%20the%20January%2022%20'pran%20pratishtha'%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Diyas'%20(earthen%20lamps)%20will%20be%20lit%20at%20all%20the%20temples%20and%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%20epic%20Ramayana%20will%20also%20take%20place%20while%20people%20will%20sing%20Ram%20bhajans%20on%20the%20day%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20put%20up%20big%20screens%20where%20the%20devotees%20will%20see%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20live.%20We%20have%20made%20arrangements%20for%20lighting%20diyas%20and%20prasad%20will%20also%20be%20distributed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20VHP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChampat%20Rai%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20said%20Ayutthaya%20is%20the%20Ayodhya%20of%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20received%20holy%20soil%20and%20water%20from%20the%20rivers%20there%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwami%20Vigyanand%2C%20founder%20and%20global%20chairman%20of%20the%20World%20Hindu%20Foundation%20(WHF)%20said%20Ayutthaya%20is%20named%20after%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20establishing%20a%20connection%20with%20Hinduism%20and%20the%20Ramayana.%20%26quot%3BKing%20Ramathibodi%2C%20the%20first%20ruler%20of%20Ayutthaya%2C%20named%20the%20city%2C%20showcasing%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20Ramayana%20on%20the%20region's%20culture.%20Subsequent%20kings%2C%20including%20those%20of%20the%20Chakri%20dynasty%2C%20adopted%20the%20name%20Rama%2C%20further%20solidifying%20the%20connection%20to%20Lord%20Ram%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20makes%20Ayutthaya%20fascinating%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20here%20we%20can%20see%20that%20the%20Ramayana%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20to%20Southeast%20Asia%20by%20Buddhist%20missionaries%2C%20was%20adapted%20into%20the%20Thai%20version%20known%20as%20Ramakien.%20This%20happened%20during%20the%20Ayutthaya%20Kingdom.%20This%20is%20how%20we%20see%20the%20impact%20of%20Rama's%20life%20on%20Thai%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Historic%20City%20of%20Phra%20Nakhon%20Si%20Ayutthaya%20(official%20name)%2C%20founded%20in%201350%2C%20was%20the%20second%20capital%20of%20the%20Siamese%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20established%20by%20Siamese%20King%20U%20Thong%2C%20who%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20King%20Ramathibodhi.%20It%20flourished%20from%20the%2014th%20to%20the%2018th%20centuries%2C%20during%20which%20time%20it%20grew%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20and%20most%20cosmopolitan%20urban%20areas%20and%20a%20centre%20of%20global%20diplomacy%20and%20commerce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20was%20attacked%20and%20razed%20by%20the%20Burmese%20army%20in%201767%20who%20burnt%20it%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20forced%20the%20inhabitants%20to%20abandon%20the%20city.%20It%20was%20never%20rebuilt%20in%20the%20same%20location%20and%20remains%20an%20archaeological%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20an%20important%20centre%20of%20global%20diplomacy%20and%20commerce%2C%20Ayutthaya%20is%20now%20an%20archaeological%20ruin%2C%20characterised%20by%20the%20remains%20of%20tall%20prang%20(reliquary%20towers)%20and%20Buddhist%20monasteries%20of%20monumental%20proportions%2C%20which%20give%20an%20idea%20of%20the%20city's%20past%20size%20and%20the%20splendour%20of%20its%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEminent%20Sanskrit%20scholar%20and%20Padma%20Bhushan%20awardee%20Satya%20Vrat%20Shastri%20has%20translated%20the%20Thai%20Ramakien%20in%20Sanskrit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ramakien%20does%20not%20necessarily%20follow%20the%20Valmiki-Ramayana%20or%20other%20versions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Rama%20story.%20It%20takes%20an%20independent%20line%20in%20a%20number%20of%20cases%20by%20introducing%20new%20episodes%20not%20figuring%20in%20the%20former%2C%26quot%3B%20Shastri%20had%20said%20in%20the%20description%20of%20his%20book%20%26quot%3BRamayana%20in%20South%20East%20Asia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Suresh%20Pal%20Giri%2C%20an%20Indian%20professor%20in%20Thailand%2C%20when%20Burmese%20soldiers%20overran%20this%20city%20in%20the%2018th%20century%2C%20a%20new%20king%20rose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20called%20himself%20Rama%20I%2C%20established%20the%20city%20now%20known%20as%20Bangkok%2C%20wrote%20the%20epic%20Ramakien%2C%20which%20is%20Ramayana%20in%20the%20local%20language%2C%20making%20it%20the%20national%20epic%2C%20and%20got%20it%20painted%20as%20murals%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20Emerald%20Buddha%2C%20patronised%20by%20the%20royal%20family%2C%20it%20is%20believed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20he%20was%20a%20Buddhist%2C%20the%20king%20established%20his%20royal%20credentials%20by%20identifying%20himself%20with%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20who%20was%20as%20much%20a%20hero%20for%20Buddhists%20of%20Southeast%20Asia%20as%20he%20was%20for%20the%20Hindus%20of%20South%20Asia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20connection%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20not%20just%20limited%20to%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Ayodhya%20but%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20the%20festivals%20and%20cultural%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20celebrates%20Kartik%20Poornima%20and%20Dev%20Deepawali%2C%20Thailand%20also%20marks%20Loy%20Krathong%2C%20known%20as%20Thailand's%20festival%20of%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20prominent%20places%2C%20the%20idols%20of%20Shiva%2C%20Parvati%2C%20Ganesha%2C%20and%20Indra%2C%20among%20others%2C%20are%20installed%2C%20where%20people%20pay%20their%20devotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Suvarnabhumi%20airport%20in%20Bangkok%20also%20has%20huge%20sculptures%20depicting%20%26quot%3BSamudra%20manthana%26quot%3B%20detailed%20in%20the%20Vishnu%20Purana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Ayuthhaya%2C%20the%20Hindu%20temples%20in%20Thailand%20are%20gearing%20up%20for%20grand%20celebrations%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20nearing%20completion%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20take%20part%20in%20its%20consecration%20ceremony%20on%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20delivered%20a%20historic%20verdict%20in%202019%2C%20settling%20a%20temple-mosque%20dispute%20that%20dated%20back%20more%20than%20a%20century.%20The%20court%20backed%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20at%20the%20disputed%20site%20and%20ruled%20that%20an%20alternative%20five-acre%20plot%20must%20be%20found%20for%20building%20a%20mosque.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%2