C%22Mohammad%20Nabi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1313-mohammad-nabi-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Nabi%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeing%20the%20latter%20decided%20to%20take%20an%20extra%20double%20after%20a%20throw%20from%20wicket-keeper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanju%20Samson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1701-sanju-samson-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESanju%20Samson%3C%2Fa%3E%20hit%20him%20and%20deflected.%20Rohit%20wasn't%20happy%20seeing%20Nabi%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20deflected%20throw%2C%20bringing%20the%20sportsmanship%20angle.%20However%2C%20veteran%20India%20spinner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20an%20intriguing%20take%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%2C%20who%20has%20been%20unofficially%20given%20the%20title%20of%20the%20sport's%20sportsmanship%20custodian%2C%20has%20often%20sided%20with%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20game%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20non-striker's%20run-out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20however%2C%20Ashwin%20donned%20the%20hat%20of%20an%20Indian%20fan%20as%20well%20as%20he%20brought%20forth%20all%20angles%20to%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20two%20sides%20to%20this%20story.%20If%20we%20are%20the%20affected%20party%20on%20the%20field%2C%20we%20will%20get%20very%20irritated%20with%20whatever%20happens.%20We%20would%20say%20we%20might%20not%20have%20done%20this%20if%20we%20were%20on%20the%20field.%20That%20is%20our%20personal%20opinion%20and%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSrrG2mqJ9NM%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20an%20Indian%20cricket%20fan%20I%20can%20say%20this%20-%20tomorrow%2C%20if%20we%20are%20facing%20a%20Super%20Over%20in%20a%20World%20Cup%20knockout%20match%2C%20it%20is%20two%20runs%20to%20win%20off%20one%20ball%20and%20the%20wicketkeeper's%20throw%20deflects%20off%20our%20glove%2C%20we%20will%20also%20run.%20How%20can%20a%20player%20not%20run%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20avid%20student%20of%20the%20game%2C%20Ashwin%20doesn't%20feel%20the%20batter%20did%20anything%20wrong%20in%20taking%20those%20extra%20couple%20of%20runs.%20He%20drew%20similarities%20between%20the%20situation%20where%20a%20batter%20gets%20leg%20byes%20or%20byes%20while%20facing%20a%20bowler%20and%20the%20much-debated%20incident%20in%20the%203rd%20T20I.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20simple%20explanation%20for%20this%20will%20suffice.%20A%20bowler%20is%20bowling%20just%20to%20pick%20your%20wicket.%20If%20you%20hit%20that%20ball%20then%20you%20can%20score%20a%20run.%20When%20the%20ball%20hits%20the%20pads%2C%20it's%20a%20leg%20bye.%20When%20it%20doesn't%20meet%20your%20body%2C%20and%20the%20keeper%20leaves%20it%2C%20it%20is%20a%20bye.%20When%20the%20ball%20goes%20wide%20off%20the%20crease%2C%20it%20is%20wide.%20When%20the%20bowler%20outstretches%20the%20leg%2C%20it%20is%20no-ball.%20All%20these%20happens%20when%20the%20bowler%20is%20trying%20to%20take%20someone's%20wicket%20and%20the%20run%20comes%20off%20the%20delivery.%20In%20the%20same%20way%2C%20when%20a%20fielder%20throws%2C%20why%20do%20they%20do%20it%3F%20To%20get%20you%20run%20out%20I%20am%20running%2C%20that%20throw%20deflects%20off%20me%2C%20I%20am%20within%20my%20right%20to%20run.%20Spirit%20of%20cricket%3F%20Yet%20again%2C%20I'm%20sorry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705649640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ficietko_ashwin-youtube_625x300_19_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-afghanistan-t20i-2024%2Fspirit-of-cricket-yet-again-i-am-sorry-r-ashwins-million-dollar-take-on-3rd-t20i-controversy-4890738%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Veteran%20India%20cricketer%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20gave%20an%20intriguing%20explanation%20of%20the%20much-debated%20Super%20Over%20incident%20involving%20India's%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Afghanistan's%20Mohammad%20Nabi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2211-Month-Old%20Baby%20In%20Hong%20Kong%20Dies%20After%20Choking%20On%20Milk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%2011-month-old%20baby%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20died%20after%20choking%20on%20milk%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20baby%20boy's%20mother%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20woman%2C%20called%20the%20police%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon%20after%20the%2011-month-old%20appeared%20to%20have%20choked%20while%20drinking%20milk%20and%20had%20lost%20consciousness.%20The%20baby%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20by%20emergency%20services%20who%20arrived%20at%20the%20home%20in%20the%20city's%20San%20Po%20Kong%20area.%20However%2C%20despite%20the%20efforts%20of%20hospital%20staff%2C%20the%20boy%20died%20soon%20after.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fsociety%2Farticle%2F3248830%2F11-month-old-hong-kong-boy-dies-hospital-after-choking-milk-home%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20baby%20had%20been%20suffering%20from%20a%20cold%20and%20fever%20and%20saw%20a%20doctor%20two%20days%20before%20the%20incident.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20mother%20was%20feeding%20him%20milk%20when%20he%20began%20vomiting.%20She%20patted%20him%20on%20the%20back%2C%20but%20he%20soon%20lost%20consciousness%2C%20prompting%20her%20to%20call%20for%20help.%20The%20incident%20is%20now%20under%20investigation%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoking%20is%20a%20potential%20concern%20for%20infants%20and%20toddlers%2C%20as%20their%20developing%20swallowing%20reflexes%20may%20not%20be%20fully%20coordinated.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fbaby%2Fbaby-choking-on-milk%23takeaway%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHealthline%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20most%20common%20reason%20a%20baby%20chokes%20during%20breastfeeding%20is%20that%20milk%20is%20coming%20out%20faster%20than%20the%20baby%20can%20swallow.%20If%20the%20baby%20is%20gagging%20when%20drinking%20from%20a%20bottle%2C%20it%20is%20often%20due%20to%20the%20positions%2C%20experts%20said.%20Common%20signs%20of%20oversupply%20include%20restlessness%20at%20the%20breast%2C%20coughing%2C%20choking%2C%20or%20gulping%20milk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20the%20baby%20from%20choking%20on%20breastmilk%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20you%20can%20do%20is%20change%20the%20feeding%20position.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20bottle%20feeding%2C%20experts%20suggest%20using%20a%20technique%20called%20paced%20bottle%20feeding.%20This%20technique%20allows%20your%20baby%20to%20actively%20pull%20milk%20out%20of%20the%20bottle%20using%20their%20sucking%20skills%20and%20lets%20them%20easily%20take%20a%20break%20when%20needed%2C%20the%20outlet%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-suffers-brain-damage-after-doctor-overdoses-her-on-fentanyl-4891200%5C%22%3EUS%20Woman%20Suffers%20Brain%20Damage%20After%20Doctor%20Overdoses%20Her%20On%20Fentanyl%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20another%20similar%20incident%2C%20a%205-month-old%20baby%20girl%20in%20Brazil%20died%20after%20choking%20on%20milk%20at%20a%20daycare%20facility.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewsweek%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20last%20year%20in%20September.%20The%20baby%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20where%20the%20doctor%20attempted%20to%20resuscitate%20the%20child%20after%20noting%20signs%20of%20milk%20aspiration%20and%20cardiorespiratory%20arrest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20aspiration%20occurs%20when%20something%20enters%20the%20lungs%20or%20airways%20by%20accident.%20This%20can%20occur%20with%20liquid%2C%20food%20and%20any%20other%20materials%20that%20are%20ingested.%20It%20can%20cause%20serious%20health%20issues.%20It%20is%20more%20common%20in%20children%2C%20particularly%20young%20ones%20and%20premature%20babies%2C%20who%20may%20have%20trouble%20swallowing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705649640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fycjolqg6h7_baby-generic-pixabay-650_625x300.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F11-month-old-baby-in-hong-kong-dies-after-choking-on-milk-4891583%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%2011-month-old%20baby%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20died%20after%20choking%20on%20milk%2C%20according%20to%20South%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F11-month-old-baby-in-hong-kong-dies-after-choking-on-milk-4891583%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F11-month-old-baby-in-hong-kong-dies-after-choking-on-milk-4891583%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F11-month-old-baby-in-hong-kong-dies-after-choking-on-milk-4891583%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Macy's%20To%20Fire%202%2C350%20Employees%2C%20Close%205%20Stores%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELeading%20department%20store%20chain%20Macy's%20could%20lay%20off%202%2C350%20employees%20and%20close%20five%20stores%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20cut%20costs%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%20(WSJ)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20job%20cuts%20will%20be%203.5%20per%20cent%20of%20Macy's%20overall%20workforce%2C%20excluding%20seasonal%20hires%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said%2C%20citing%20an%20internal%20memo%20sent%20to%20employees%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20overall%20plan%20is%20to%20fire%2013%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20corporate%20staff%20and%20redirect%20the%20money%20saved%20to%20improve%20shopping%20experience%20for%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20adding%20more%20automation%20to%20its%20supply%20chain%20and%20outsourcing%20some%20role%2C%20but%20Macy's%20hasn't%20specify%20which%20jobs%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fretail%2Fmacys-to-cut-about-2-350-jobs-close-five-stores-f7daac9d%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWSJ%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFresh%20investments%20will%20include%20adding%20more%20visual%20display%20managers%20to%20enhance%20the%20look%20of%20stores%20and%20upgrading%20digital%20functions%20to%20make%20online%20shopping%20more%20seamless%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20development%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20comes%20a%20month%20before%20Macy's%20President%20Tony%20Spring%20takes%20over%20as%20CEO%20from%20Jeff%20Gennette.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20facing%20pressure%20from%20investors%20who%20have%20launched%20a%20%245.8%20billion%20bid%20to%20buy%20the%20department%20store%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20our%20strong%20and%20tangible%20progress%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20we%20remain%20under%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gennette%20said%20in%20the%20memo%20accessed%20by%20WSJ.%20He%20informed%20the%20employees%20that%20the%20move%20is%20a%20response%20to%20nearly%20a%20year%20of%20consumer%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20owns%20Bloomingdale's%20department%20stores%20and%20Bluemercury%20beauty%20and%20skin-care%20shops.%20Macy's%20has%20not%20said%20anything%20officially%2C%20but%20is%20expected%20to%20provide%20a%20response%20in%20coming%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacy's%20is%20the%20latest%20to%20join%20the%20list%20of%20companies%20that%20have%20announced%20job%20cuts%20this%20year.%20Sundar%20Pichai%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20tech%20giant%20Google%2C%20told%20employees%20to%20expect%20more%20job%20cuts%2C%20a%20week%20after%20announcing%20lay-offs%20in%20its%20Voice%20Assistant%20units%2C%20hardware%20teams%20responsible%20for%20Pixel%2C%20Nest%20and%20Fitbit%2C%20advertising%20sales%20team%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20its%20augmented%20reality%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pichai%20said%20the%20lay-offs%20were%20focused%20on%20removing%20layers%20to%20simplify%20execution%20and%20drive%20velocity%20in%20some%20areas%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Verge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Reuters%20report%20said%20that%20tech%20firms%2C%20including%20Google%20and%20Amazon%2C%20have%20let%20go%20more%20than%207%2C500%20employees%20so%20far%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705649580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-05%2Fmacy-mall_650x400_41525343766.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmacys-to-fire-2-350-employees-close-5-stores-report-4891577%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Macy's%20has%20not%20said%20anything%20officially%2C%20but%20is%20expected%20to%20provide%20a%20response%20in%20coming%20weeks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmacys-to-fire-2-350-employees-close-5-stores-report-4891577%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmacys-to-fire-2-350-employees-close-5-stores-report-4891577%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmacys-to-fire-2-350-employees-close-5-stores-report-4891577%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Photo%20Of%20Ram%20Lalla%20Idol%20Revealed%20Ahead%20Of%20Consecration%20Ceremony%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20placed%20inside%20Ayodhya's%20Ram%20Temple%20yesterday%20ahead%20of%20the%20'pran%20pratis