%5C%22%3EJaish%20al-Adl%3C%2Fa%3E%20group%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20it%20says%20has%20links%20to%20Islamic%20State.%20Many%20of%20Jaish's%20members%20previously%20belonged%20to%20a%20now-defunct%20terror%20group%20known%20as%20Jundallah%20that%20had%20pledged%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Islamic%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20suggest%20that%20the%20recent%20strike%20on%20Pakistan%20was%20primarily%20driven%20by%20Iran's%20internal%20security%20concerns%20rather%20than%20ambitions%20for%20regional%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20said%20it%20had%20for%20years%20complained%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-air-strikes-in-iran-after-strikes-pakistan-says-had-info-on-large-scale-terror-activities-in-iran-4884384%5C%22%3Eterrorists%20had%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20havens%20and%20sanctuaries%26quot%3B%20in%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20and%20was%20forced%20to%20take%20matters%20into%20its%20own%20hands%20with%20Thursday's%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20has%20heightened%20concerns%20about%20the%20stability%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20which%20have%20been%20escalating%20since%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20in%20October.%20Iran-backed%20militias%2C%20extending%20from%20Yemen%20to%20Lebanon%2C%20have%20carried%20out%20attacks%20on%20US%20and%20Israeli%20targets%2C%20including%20incidents%20involving%20Red%20Sea%20shipping%2C%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20their%20statements%2C%20after%20the%20tit-for-tat%20blows%2C%20neither%20government%20sought%20to%20make%20a%20link%20to%20the%20Gaza%20war%20or%20to%20attacks%20carried%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Palestinians%20by%20a%20network%20of%20Arab%20militias%20allied%20to%20Iran%20from%20the%20Mediterranean%20to%20the%20Gulf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20say%20that%20Iran's%20actions%20are%20not%20isolated%20but%20are%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20regional%20conflict%20where%