0Gaza%2C%20described%20gunfire%20and%20air%20strikes.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20targeted%20this%20area%2C%20claiming%20it%20as%20a%20stronghold%20for%20members%20and%20leaders%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Red%20Crescent%20reported%20intense%20artillery%20fire%20near%20Al-Amal%20hospital%2C%20with%20Gaza's%20health%20ministry%2C%20under%20Hamas%20control%2C%20confirming%2077%20deaths%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military's%20Givati%20Brigade%20engaged%20in%20close-quarters%20combat%2C%20using%20tank%20fire%20and%20air%20support%2C%20claiming%20the%20elimination%20of%20dozens%20of%20terrorists%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20warns%20that%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%2C%20which%20began%20with%20Hamas%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20has%20displaced%20approximately%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20Gaza's%202.4%20million%20population.%20Many%20are%20now%20crammed%20into%20shelters%2C%20facing%20challenges%20in%20accessing%20essential%20resources%20like%20food%2C%20water%2C%20fuel%2C%20and%20medical%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20reported%2024%20cases%20of%20hepatitis%20A%20and%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20jaundice%20cases%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20improved%20aid%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Hamas's%20attacks%20on%20October%207%2C%20casualties%20in%20Israel%20stand%20at%20around%201%2C140%2C%20mostly%20civilians.%20Militants%20also%20took%20hostages%2C%20with%20some%20still%20held%20in%20Gaza.%20Israel%20claims%20that%20at%20least%2027%20hostages%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Israel%20has%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bannihilate%26quot%3B%20Hamas%2C%20launching%20relentless%20air%20and%20ground%20offensives.%20The%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20reports%20at%20least%2024%2C620%20Palestinian%20casualties%2C%20comprising%20approximately%2070%20percent%20women%2C%20children%2C%20and%20adolescents.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705647540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Feu7v1ggg_gaza-university-bombing-_625x300_19_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-university-video-israel-allegedly-bombs-gaza-university-us-asks-for-clarity-4891392%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20video%20allegedly%20showing%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20targeting%20Palestine%20University's%20main%20campus%20building%20in%20Gaza%20is%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-university-video-israel-allegedly-bombs-gaza-university-us-asks-for-clarity-4891392%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-university-video-israel-allegedly-bombs-gaza-university-us-asks-for-clarity-4891392%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-university-video-israel-allegedly-bombs-gaza-university-us-asks-for-clarity-4891392%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Main%20Atal%20Hoon%20-%20Single-Note%20Biography%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20movie%20industry%20rarely%2C%20if%20ever%2C%20does%20justice%20to%20biopics%2C%20be%20they%20of%20personalities%20of%20contemporary%20relevance%20or%20of%20figures%20of%20historical%20significance.%20%3Ci%3EMain%20Atal%20Hoon%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20helmed%20and%20co-written%20by%20the%20National%20Award-winning%20director%20Ravi%20Jadhav%20(%3Cem%3ENatarang%2C%20Balgandharva%2C%20Balak%20Palak%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20does%20little%20to%20change%20that%20widely%20held%20belief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20not%20a%20botched%20effort%20without%20any%20redeeming%20features%2C%20%3Cem%3EMain%20Atal%20Hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%20carries%20creases%20that%20could%20have%20been%20avoided%20had%20the%20film%20not%20been%20such%20a%20rushed%20exercise.%20The%20hurry%20to%20wrap%20it%20up%20in%20time%20has%20clearly%20had%20a%20bearing%20both%20on%20the%20writing%20and%20the%20making.%20Jadhav%20is%20known%20to%20be%20a%20director%20with%20an%20eye%20for%20detail.%20That%20trait%20is%20conspicuous%20by%20its%20absence%20in%20%3Cem%3EMain%20Atal%20Hoon.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20hagiography%20than%20homage%2C%20%3Cem%3EMain%20Atal%20Hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%20employs%20a%20from-the-cradle-to-the-grave%20approach%20to%20tell%20the%20story%20of%20the%20life%20of%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20luminary%20and%20India's%20tenth%20Prime%20Minister.%20That%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20the%20patchy%20film%20straddles%20the%20entire%20spectrum%20of%20the%20rightwing%20leader's%20boyhood%20years%20and%20eventful%20political%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20presents%20a%20bit%20of%20this%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20that%20as%20it%20flits%20from%20one%20high%20point%20to%20another%20in%20crafting%20a%20picture%20designed%20to%20evoke%20awe%20and%20reverence.%20The%20strategy%20works%20neither%20as%20drama%20nor%20as%20cinema%20because%20whatever%20conflict%20there%20is%20in%20the%20tale%20is%20studiously%20underplayed%20in%20order%20to%20emphasize%20how%20undeterred%20and%20unbudging%20(the%20accent%20being%20on%20the%20leader's%20given%20name%2C%20'Atal')%20Vajpayee%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMain%20Atal%20Hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20aspects%20of%20Vajpayee's%20life%20and%20times%20that%20serve%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20prevalent%20political%20climate%20but%20it%20is%20unable%20to%20put%20together%20a%20truly%20dramatic%20portrait%20of%20a%20statesman%20and%20an%20orator%20who%20encountered%20many%20ups%20and%20downs%20and%20ebbs%20and%20tides%20in%20the%20course%20of%20a%20long%20journey%20through%20the%20tumult%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20the%20vicissitudes%20of%20nation-building%20and%20the%20challenges%20of%20party%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMain%20Atal%20Hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20single-note%20biography%20salvaged%20a%20touch%20-%20only%20a%20touch%20-%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fif-mukesh-ambani-was-not-a-businessman-pankaj-tripathi-on-stereotypes-in-bollywood-4834783%5C%22%3EPankaj%20Tripathi's%3C%2Fa%3E%20central%20performance.%20The%20actor%20spares%20no%20effort%20to%20get%20into%20the%20skin%20of%20Vajpayee%20and%20imitating%20his%20body%20language%20and%20speaking%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETripathi's%20efforts%20do%20not%20bear%20the%20expected%20fruit%20because%20the%20screenplay%20on%20which%20the%20performance%20stands%20is%20hobbled%20by%20a%20lack%20of%20imagination%20and%20true%20insight.%20The%20blend%20of%20humanity%20and%20political%20expediency%2C%20political%20acumen%20and%20communication%20skills%20would%20have%20yielded%20much%20greater%20dividends%20had%20Jadhav%20and%20co-writer%20Rishi%20Virmani%20focused%20more%20on%20the%20questions%20that%20Vajpayee%20faced%20than%20on%20the%20answers%20that%20he%20found%20and%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMain%20Atal%20Hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%20meanders%20from%20one%20thing%20to%20another%2C%20intent%20solely%20on%20talking%20up%20the%20deeds%20that%20the%20real-life%20protagonist%20performed%20as%20a%20politician%20and%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20complexities%20of%20subcontinental%20politics%20and%20the%20intricacies%20of%20ideological%20warfare%20in%20Parliament%20and%20outside%20of%20it%20are%20well%20beyond%20this%20film's%20limited%20purview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20settles%20for%20simplistic%20and%20reductionist%20methods%20that%20take%20all%20the%20sharp%20edges%20away.%20Vajpayee's%20initiative%20to%20foster%20friendship%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20and%20his%20journey%20on%20the%20Delhi-Lahore%20bus%20to%20attend%20a%20summit%20finds%20space%20in%20the%20narrative.%20However%2C%20his%20peacenik%20persona%20is%20allowed%20to%20be%20a%20mere%20footnote%20in%20a%20film%20that%20has%20been%20made%20to%20propagate%20a%20particular%20set%20of%20beliefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allusion%20to%20the%20Kargil%20victory%20-%20it%20in%20now%20celebrated%20as%20Kargil%20Vijay%20Diwas%20-%20would%20have%20translated%20into%20something%20more%20substantial%20than%20it%20does%20in%20this%20film%20had%20it%20also%20factored%20in%2C%20if%20only%20in%20passing%2C%20the%20intelligence%20failure%20that%20led%20to%20the%20border%20conflict%20and%20its%20human%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20casting%20of%20Pankaj%20Tripathi%20as%20the%20politician%20is%20anything%20but%20perfect%20in%20terms%20of%20physical%20verisimilitude%2C%20but%20the%20actor%20manages%20to%20tide%20over%20the%20question%20of%20authenticity%20with%20a%20turn%20that%20comes%20pretty%20close%20to%20being%20perfect%20within%20the%20limitations%20imposed%20by%20the%20way%20the%20role%20has%20been%20conceived%20by%20the%20writers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20a%20Marathi%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3ESarang%20Darshane's%20Atalji%3A%20Kavihridayache%20Rashtranetyachi%20Charitkahani%20(The%20Story%20of%20a%20Poet-Leader%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20%3Cem%3EMain%20Atal%20Hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20literal%20depiction%20of%20Vajpayee%20as%20a%20poet%20and%20a%20politician%20endowed%20with%20outstanding%20oratorial%20flair.%20It%20is%20the%20latter%20persona%20that%20the%20lead%20actor%20brings%20out%20particularly%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FVhXP6RDqb1k%3Fsi%3DQsq90LUbOCyILe43%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWould%20%3Cem%3EMain%20Atal%20Hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%20been%20a%20markedly%20different%20film%20had%20the%20makers%20not%20been%20slavishly%20led%20by%20the%20book's%20title%20and%20dared%20to%20draw%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20a%20politician%20with%20a%20poet's%20temperament%2C%20a%20man%20who%20grew%20up%20with%20a%20love%20for%20the%20Hindi%20language%20and%20attained%20mastery%20over%20it%2C%20is%20a%20rarity%20in%20politics%3F%20No%20question%20about%20it%20-%20that%20would%20have%20led%20to%20a%20more%20rewarding%20film.%20But%2C%20then%2C%20it%20would%20not%20have%20served%20the%20avowed%20purpose%20of%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivered%20mostly%20with%20broad%20strokes%20that%20dwell%20on%20Vajpayee's%20personal%20associations%20and%20political%20affiliations%2C%20the%20film%20skims%20over%20many%20significant%20details%20and%20nuances%20that%20might%20have%20added%20up%20to%20an%20infinitely%20more%20rounded%2C%20analytical%20and%20dispassionate%20portrait%20rather%20than%20the%20unalloyed%20paean%20that%20it%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20elements%20in%20the%20film%20that%20had%20tremendous%20potential%20-%20Vajpayee's%20relationship%20with%20his%20father%20(played%20by%20Piyush%20Mishra)%20and%20his%20lasting%20friendship%20with%20Rajkumari%20Kaul%20(Ekta%20Kaul)%20are%20cases%20in%20point%20-%20but%20the%20script%20deigns%20to%20treat%20them%20the%20way%20it%20treats%20everything%20else%20at%20its%20disposal%2C%20as%20just%20a%20piece%20to%20fit%20into%20the%20larger%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20purely%20cinematic%20sense%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20be%20enthused%20over%20what%20%3Cem%3EMain%20Atal%20Hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20to%20offer.%20But%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20film's%20undisguised%20raison%20d'etre%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20a%20total%20washout.%20It%20might%20find%20takers%20beyond%20the%20folds%20of%20those%20who%20demand%20greater%20critical%20depth%20and%20range%20in%20Bollywood%20biopics%20only%20to%20be%20disappointed%20time%20after%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705647540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F98hplu4g_mai-atal-hu_625x300_19_January_24.jpeg%22