r%20escalation%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20that%20the%20country%20has%20noted%20the%20Pakistani%20government's%20comments%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20%26quot%3Bcooperative%20relations%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20its%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20question%20on%20how%20the%20US%20administration%20reads%20the%20situation%20between%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20Miller%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20concerned%20about%20escalating%20tensions%20in%20the%20region.%20It's%20been%20something%20we%20have%20spoken%20a%20number%20of%20times%2C%20we've%20focused%20on.%20We've%20been%20incredibly%20concerned%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20escalation%20since%20October%207.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20we%20have%20engaged%20in%20intense%20diplomatic%20efforts%20to%20try%20to%20prevent%20escalation.%20We%20noted%20the%20comments%20from%20the%20government%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20cooperative%20relations%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20its%20neighbours.%20We%20thought%20those%20were%20productive%20useful%20statements%2C%20and%20certainly%2C%20there's%20no%20need%20for%20escalation%20and%20we%20would%20urge%20restraint%20on%20all%20sides%20in%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Miller%20called%20Iran%20a%20major%20funder%20of%20Hezbollah%20and%20a%20principal%20supporter%20of%20Hamas%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20query%20about%20the%20ongoing%20tensions%20between%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan%20after%20strikes%20and%20counterstrikes%2C%20Miller%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20made%20pretty%20clear%20yesterday%20what%20we%20think%20about%20Iran's%20attacks%2C%20not%20just%20the%20strikes%20that%20were%20launched%20in%20the%20past%20three%20days%20against%20three%20of%20its%20neighbours%20but%20its%20long%20history%20of%20funding%20terrorism%2C%20funding%20instability%20and%20sowing%20discord%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20That's%20something%20we%20have%20seen%20contribute%20to%20conflict%20in%20Gaza.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20strikes%20in%20Pakistan%20came%20after%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC)%20launched%20missiles%20into%20Iraq's%20Kurdistan%20region%20at%20what%20it%20called%20an%20Israeli%20%26quot%3Bspy%20headquarters%26quot%3B%20and%20at%20alleged%20ISIS-linked%20targets%20in%20Syria%2C%20Al%20Arabiya%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Pakistan%20on%20Thursday%20launched%20missile%20strikes%20into%20Iran%20and%20codenamed%20it%20operation%20'Marg%20Bar%20Sarmachar'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20(MoFA)%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20it%20had%20undertaken%20a%20series%20of%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20coordinated%20and%20specifically%20targeted%20precision%20military%20strikes%20against%20terrorist%20hideouts%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Siestan-o-Baluchistan%20province%20of%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20number%20of%20terrorists%20were%20killed%20during%20the%20intelligence-based%20operation%20codenamed%20%26quot%3BMarg%20Bar%20Sarmachar%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20US%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20Miller%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20seen%20Iran%20as%20the%20principal%20supporter%20of%20Hamas%20for%20years.%20They%20are%20the%20major%20funder%20of%20Hezbollah.%20They%20are%20one%20of%20the%20major%20funders%20of%20the%20Houthis.%20We%20have%20seen%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20actions%20that%20Iran%20has%20taken%20to%20add%20to%20regional%20instability%20and%20that's%20why%20we%20continue%20to%20take%20actions%20to%20hold%20Iran%20accountable%20and%20also%20send%20clear%20very%20messages%20to%20Iran%20that%20we%20don't%20believe%20this%20should%20escalate%20in%20any%20way%2C%20shape%20or%20form.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20is%20a%20major%20non-NATO%20ally%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20that%20will%20remain%20the%20case%2C%20but%20we%20would%20urge%20restraint%20in%20this%20case.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20to%20see%20escalation%20and%20don't%20think%20there's%20a%20need%20for%20escalation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20National%20Security%20Council%20Coordinator%20for%20Strategic%20Communications%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20John%20Kirby%2C%20said%20the%20US%20is%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20regarding%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan%20%26quot%3Bvery%20very%20closely%26quot%3B%20and%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%20see%20escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705644840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Frl08edmg_iran-pakistan-afp-_625x300_19_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdid-pakistan-consult-washington-before-iran-strike-us-evades-question-4891156%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20on%20Thursday%20evaded%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20Pakistan%20held%20prior%20consultations%20with%20Washington%20before%20conducting%20retaliatory%20air%20strikes%20on%20Iran.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdid-pakistan-consult-washington-before-iran-strike-us-evades-question-4891156%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdid-pakistan-consult-washington-before-iran-strike-us-evades-question-4891156%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdid-pakistan-consult-washington-before-iran-strike-us-evades-question-4891156%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20Consumer%20Products%20to%20raise%20%24782%20mn%20through%20issue%20of%20commercial%20papers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705644783000%2C%22visual%22%3A%