or%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnato-to-hold-biggest-drills-since-cold-war-with-90000-troops%2Farticleshow%2F106977640.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnato-to-hold-biggest-drills-since-cold-war-with-90000-troops%2Famp_articleshow%2F106977640.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnato-to-hold-biggest-drills-since-cold-war-with-90000-troops%2Famp_articleshow%2F106977640.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20North%20Korea's%20Kim%20Is%20Preparing%20For%20War%20On%20South%20Korea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20has%20declared%20the%20South%20his%20country's%20%26quot%3Bprincipal%20enemy%26quot%3B%2C%20jettisoned%20agencies%20dedicated%20to%20reunification%20and%20outreach%2C%20and%20threatened%20war%20over%20%26quot%3Beven%200.001%20mm%26quot%3B%20of%20territorial%20infringement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20is%20the%20fiery%20rhetoric%20a%20sign%20of%20a%20real%20shift%3F%20AFP%20takes%20a%20look%20at%20what%20we%20know%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat's%20happened%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20worsening%20ties%2C%20Pyongyang%20made%20it%20official%20this%20week%3A%20declaring%20Seoul%20its%20main%20enemy%2C%20abolishing%20agencies%20dedicated%20to%20reunification%20and%20threatening%20to%20occupy%20the%20South%20during%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20big%20shift%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20past%20when%20there%20was%20risk%20of%20an%20armed%20conflict%2C%20there%20was%20a%20back%20channel%20to%20keep%20it%20in%20control%2C%20but%20now%20there%20is%20none%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hong%20Min%2C%20a%20senior%20analyst%20at%20the%20Korea%20Institute%20for%20National%20Unification%20in%20Seoul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korea%20has%20gotten%20rid%20%26quot%3Bof%20any%20inter-Korean%20mechanisms%20to%20prevent%20conflicts%20from%20spiralling%20out%20of%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20North's%20labeling%20of%20the%20South%20as%20its%20'principal%20enemy'%20isn't%20just%20rhetorical%20--%20the%20words%20could%20carry%20into%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWill%20he%20invade%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKim%20said%20he%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20starting%20a%20war%20--%20but%20also%20none%20of%20avoiding%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe's%20declared%20he%20will%20no%20longer%20recognise%20the%20de%20facto%20maritime%20border%20between%20the%20two%20Koreas%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Northern%20Limit%20Line%2C%20and%20his%20military%20recently%20staged%20days%20of%20live-fire%20artillery%20drills%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20created%20%26quot%3Ba%20growing%20possibility%20of%20the%20two%20sides%20getting%20into%20a%20military%20skirmish%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20wider%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Hong%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20Pyongyang%20has%20been%20drawing%20closer%20to%20Moscow%2C%20including%20--%20Washington%20and%20Seoul%20claim%20--%20sending%20missiles%20for%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20in%20exchange%20for%20help%20with%20their%20satellite%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeoul%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20has%20threatened%20a%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20times%20stronger%26quot%3B%20response%20to%20any%20provocation%2C%20a%20hawkish%20approach%20that%20carries%20risks%20as%20an%20editorial%20in%20the%20Hankyoreh%20newspaper%20pointed%20out%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20never%20wise%20for%20both%20South%20and%20North%20Korea%20to%20take%20a%20no-prisoners%20approach%20in%20inter-Korea%20dealings%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20North%20Korea%20becomes%20more%20reckless%2C%20we%20hope%20that%20the%20government%20will%20focus%20its%20efforts...%20to%20manage%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat's%20next%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Koreas%20are%20now%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20highest%20probability%20of%20being%20dragged%20into%20armed%20conflict%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Choi%20Gi-il%2C%20professor%20of%20military%20studies%20at%20Sangji%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20civilian%20and%20military%20casualties%20incur%20from%20a%20future%20Northern%20provocation.%20We%20target%20the%20point%20of%20origin%20with%20shells.%20But%20will%20we%20also%20strike%20them%20with%20air%20power%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20when%20the%20North%20shelled%20the%20remote%20South%20Korean%20border%20island%20of%20Yeonpyeong%2C%20killing%20four%2C%20Seoul's%20F-16%20jets%20were%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20air%20ready%20to%20strike%20but%20then-president%20Lee%20Myung-bak%20called%20it%20off%26quot%3B%20to%20avoid%20escalating%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20we%20have%20a%20similar%20incident%2C%20there's%20no%20guarantee%20that%20air%20power%20will%20not%20be%20used%20given%20hawkish%20calls%26quot%3B%20from%20Seoul's%20administration%2C%20Choi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Pyongyang's%20response%20could%20see%20the%20peninsula%20%26quot%3Breach%20a%20full-fledged%20war%20in%20the%20worst%20case%20scenario%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ENo%20chance%20of%20rapprochement%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prospects%20for%20inter-Korean%20reconciliation%20have%20long%20been%20dim%2C%20but%20now%20Kim%20has%20told%20Seoul%20to%20its%20face%20that%20he%20views%20them%20as%20his%20number%20one%20enemy%2C%20Soo%20Kim%2C%20policy%20practice%20area%20lead%20at%20LMI%20Consulting%20and%20former%20CIA%20analyst%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20only%20closed%20the%20door%20to%20rapprochement%20--%20he's%20put%20a%20padlock%20on%20it%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20to%20the%20South%20Koreans%20where%20he%20stands%20on%20their%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20new%20rhetoric%20from%20Pyongyang%20doesn't%20necessarily%20%26quot%3Bchange%20the%20calculus%20for%20North%20Korea%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPyongyang%20has%20long%20been%20developing%20nukes%20and%20missiles%2C%20and%20Kim%20has%20been%20waiting%20for%20an%20opportune%20moment%20to%20conduct%20his%20much-anticipated%20seventh%20nuclear%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20weapons%20weren't%20developed%20overnight%2C%20and%20the%20Kim%20regime's%20plans%20to%20use%20them%20as%20tools%20of%20coercion%2C%20threats%2C%20and%20bargaining%20have%20been%20their%20modus%20operandi%20for%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhy%20is%20Kim%20doing%20this%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKim's%20new%20messaging%20on%20South%20Korea%20%26quot%3Bappears%20to%20be%20an%20ideological%20adjustment%20for%20regime%20survival%2C%20justifying%20Kim's%20focus%20on%20nuclear%20missiles%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Leif-Eric%20Easley%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Ewha%20University%20in%20Seoul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20years%20of%20Covid-linked%20border%20closures%2C%20and%20strict%20controls%20on%20the%20flow%20of%20information%20domestically%2C%20North%20Koreans%20%26quot%3Bare%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20their%20country's%20economic%20failings%20compared%20to%20South%20Korean%20successes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20Kim%20is%20doubling%20down%20on%20military%20prowess%20against%20external%20threats%20for%20his%20domestic%20legitimacy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea%20is%20also%20set%20for%20a%20general%20election%20in%20April%2C%20where%20President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol's%20party%20is%20trying%20to%20win%20back%20control%20of%20the%20country's%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKim%20may%20also%20be%20trying%20to%20politically%20punish%20the%20Yoon%20administration%20for%20its%20policies%20toward%20Pyongyang%20ahead%20of