th-malhotras-performance-shines-through-in-rohit-shettys-childish-yet-very-entertaining-web-series%2Farticleshow%2F106973501.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Calls%20Assam%20Govt%20'Most%20Corrupt'%2C%20FIR%20Against%20Yatra%20for%20'Deviating%20From%20Route'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19102403%2FGEIkjpGW8AALSAw.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20lodged%20in%20the%20Jorhat%20Sadar%20Police%20Station%2C%20Assam%20again%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20being%20led%20by%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20its%20chief%20organiser%20K.B.%20Byju%20for%20allegedly%20deviating%20from%20the%20route%20that%20had%20been%20allowed%20in%20Jorhat%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20PTI%2C%20the%20FIR%20states%20that%20the%20yatra%20did%20not%20follow%20the%20district%20administration%E2%80%99s%20norms%20and%20violated%20road%20safety%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20opposition%20in%20Assam%20Debabrata%20Saikia%20told%20PTI%20that%20this%20FIR%20was%20a%20political%20move%2C%20as%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20was%20shaken%20by%20the%20yatra%E2%80%99s%20success.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20police%20manning%20the%20traffic%20diversion%20at%20the%20PWD%20point.%20The%20assigned%20route%20was%20too%20small%20and%20we%20had%20a%20huge%20gathering.%20So%2C%20we%20took%20a%20detour%20for%20just%20a%20few%20metres.%C2%A0Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20is%20scared%20of%20the%20Yatra%E2%80%99s%20success%20on%20the%20first%20day%20(in%20Assam)%20and%20now%20wants%20to%20derail%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20Assam%2C%20Gandhi%20had%20heavily%20criticised%20the%20Sarma-led%20BJP%20government%2C%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Cperhaps%20the%20most%20corrupt%20government%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%20Addressing%20party%20workers%20at%20Halowating%20in%20Sivasagar%20district%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-assam-rahul-gandhi-attacks-himanta-led-bjp-govt-most-corrupt-in-india-101705561962495.html%5C%22%3Ehe%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CPerhaps%2C%20the%20most%20corrupt%20government%20in%20India%20is%20in%20Assam.%20We%20will%20raise%20the%20issues%20of%20Assam%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarma%20retaliated%20by%20saying%20that%20was%20in%20fact%20that%20Gandhi%20family%20that%20was%20the%20most%20corrupt.%20His%20response%20also%20came%20with%20communal%20overtones%2C%20as%20he%20said%20the%20yatra%20was%20only%20meant%20for%20%E2%80%98Miyas%E2%80%99%20(Bengali%20Muslims%20living%20in%20Assam).%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Gandhi%20family%20is%20the%20most%20corrupt%20family%20in%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20not%20%E2%80%98Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Miya%20Yatra%E2%80%99.%20Wherever%20there%20are%20Muslims%2C%20they%20visit%20those%20places%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20east%20to%20west%20yatra%20is%20the%20largest%20mass%20outreach%20programme%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20will%20travel%20around%206%2C700%20km.%20It%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpromise-to-bring-peace-says-rahul-gandhi-as-he-kicks-off-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-from-manipur%5C%22%3Estarted%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20January%2014%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Thoubal%20and%20will%20end%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Maharashtra%20on%20March%2020%20or%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705640137000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19102403%2FGEIkjpGW8AALSAw.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-rahul-gandhi-calls-assam-govt-most-corrupt-fir-against-yatra-for-deviating-from-route%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20FIR%20states%20that%20the%20yatra%20did%20not%20follow%20