ed%20the%20information%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenergycommerce.house.gov%2Fposts%2Fe-and-c-investigation-uncovers-earliest-known-sars-co-v-2-sequence-released-outside-of-china%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20House%20Energy%20%26amp%3B%20Commerce%20Committee%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20is%20significant%20because%20it%20may%20have%20wasted%20time%20for%20the%20world%20to%20develop%20COVID-19%20vaccines%20and%20treatments%2C%20causing%20needless%20deaths%2C%20the%20committee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20said%20a%20Chinese%20virologist%2C%20Lili%20Ren%2C%20submitted%20the%20pathogen's%20gene%20sequence%20to%20the%20US%20database%20GenBank%20on%20December%2028%2C%202019%2C%20the%20committee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20database%20belongs%20to%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%2C%20of%20which%20Ren%20is%20a%20subgrantee%20under%20the%20nonprofit%20EcoHealth%20Alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERen's%20submission%2C%20however%2C%20was%20missing%20some%20technical%20information%2C%20and%20the%20database%20staff%20asked%20her%20three%20days%20later%20to%20submit%20the%20additional%20details.%20If%20she%20didn't%20offer%20these%20details%2C%20the%20sequence%20would%20be%20deleted%2C%20the%20staff%20said%2C%20per%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20lawmakers%20added%20that%20Ren%20did%20not%20upload%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20necessary%20information%20to%20the%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2010%2C%202020%2C%20about%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20China%20released%20a%20gene%20sequence%20of%20COVID-19%20that%20was%20%26quot%3Bnearly%20identical%26quot%3B%20to%20Ren's%20submission%2C%20the%20committee%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20said%20this%20contradicted%20China's%20repeated%20claims%20that%20it%20released%20the%20gene%20sequence%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20obtained%20the%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20embassy%20in%20the%20US%20in%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fus.china-embassy.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fzmgxss%2F202111%2Ft20211107_10445198.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereleased%20a%20statement%20%3C%2Fa%3Eattacking%20%26quot%3BUS%20vicious%20slanders%2C%26quot%3B%20responding%20to%20dozens%20of%20allegations%20from%20US%20media%20and%20officials%20about%20Beijing's%20handling%20of%20the%20virus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20upholding%20a%20scientific%20attitude%20and%20following%20the%20laws%20of%20epidemiology%2C%20the%20Chinese%20government%20promptly%20shared%20the%20virus%20genetic%20sequence%20and%20epidemic%20information%20with%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20and%20the%20international%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20committee%20said%20this%20example%20shows%20that%20China%20has%20been%20forthcoming%20with%20sharing%20vital%20medical%20information%20for%20fighting%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20significant%20discovery%20further%20underscores%20why%20we%20cannot%20trust%20any%20of%20the%20so-called%20facts%20or%20data%20provided%20by%20the%20CCP%20and%20calls%20into%20serious%20question%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20any%20scientific%20theories%20based%20on%20such%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20investigating%20lawmakers%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20also%20raised%20concerns%20that%20the%20NIH%20had%20received%20a%20COVID-19%20gene%20sequence%20but%20%26quot%3Bapparently%20had%20no%20idea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20criticized%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20NIH%2C%20and%20HHS%2C%20saying%20the%20information%20on%20the%20sequence%20submitted%20by%20Ren%20was%20only%20released%20after%20it%20was%20subpoenaed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chairs%20of%20the%20Energy%20%26amp%3B%20Commerce%20Committee%20and%20its%20Health%20and%20Oversight%20%26amp%3B%20Investigations%20Subcommittees%2C%20which%20conducted%20the%20investigation%2C%20are%20all%20Repub