th-generation%20Intel%20Core%20CPUs%20first%20launched%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202023%2C%20and%20you%20can%20now%20find%20various%20chips%20in%20new%20prebuilt%20desktop%20and%20laptop%20models%20from%20top%20brands.%20Desktop%20CPUs%20are%20also%20available%20to%20purchase%20on%20their%20own%2C%20so%20you%20can%20use%20them%20to%20build%20your%20own%20computer.%20If%20you're%20thinking%20about%20buying%20a%20new%20Intel%2014th-gen%20chip%20or%20a%20computer%20with%20one%20built-in%2C%20here%20are%20some%20details%20you%20should%20know.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Intel%20Core%2014th%20generation%20for%20desktops%5C%22%3EIntel%20Core%2014th%20generation%20for%20desktops%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20let's%20look%20at%20Intel's%20flagship%20line%20of%20consumer-grade%20desktop%20CPUs%2C%20the%20Intel%20Core%20i5%2Fi7%2Fi9%2014th%20generation.%20The%2014th%20generation%20debuted%20in%20October%202023%20with%20the%20i9-14900K%2FKF%2C%20i7-14700K%2FKF%2C%20and%20i5-14600K%2FKF.%20These%20chips%20are%20the%20direct%20successors%20to%20the%20Intel%20Core%2013th%20generation%20and%20feature%20small%20improvements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20processors%20are%20sometimes%20known%20by%20their%20codename%2C%20%26quot%3BRaptor%20Lake.%26quot%3B%20But%20that%20name%20is%20a%20generic%20title%20used%20for%20both%20the%2014th%20and%2013th%20generations%20%E2%80%94%20the%2014th%20generation's%20unique%20name%20is%20actually%20%26quot%3BRaptor%20Lake%20Refresh.%26quot%3B%20As%20that%20name%20suggests%2C%20Intel's%20new%20chips%20are%20mostly%20a%20new%20iteration%20of%20the%20previous%20lineup%20rather%20than%20a%20full%20overhaul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20see%20this%20in%20the%2014th%20generation's%20hardware%20statistics.%20Both%20the%2013th-%20and%2014th-generation%20K%2FKF%20desktop%20chips%20have%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20performance%20cores%3B%20they%20have%20the%20same%20maximum%20memory%20size%20and%20bandwidth%2C%20and%20the%20base%20and%20%26quot%3BTurbo%26quot%3B%20clock%20rates%20have%20only%20barely%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20performance%20isn't%20much%20better%2C%20either.%20Benchmarking%20firms%20like%20Puget%20Systems%20report%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pugetsystems.com%2Flabs%2Farticles%2F14th-gen-intel-core-processors-content-creation-review%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20than%2010%25%20(and%20usually%20lower%20than%205%25)%20performance%20speed%20gains%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20tasks.%20For%20the%20i5%20and%20i7%20models%2C%20this%20is%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20higher%20number%20of%20efficiency%20cores.%20That's%20not%20a%20big%20increase%2C%20and%20for%20most%20users%2C%20not%20worth%20upgrading%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20be%20clear%2C%20both%20generations%20are%20incredibly%20powerful%2C%20with%20the%20K%2FKF-series%20desktop%20chips%20able%20to%20run%20nearly%20any%20program%20and%20multitask%20with%20ease.%20Even%20if%20the%20new%20Intel%20processors%20aren't%20vastly%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20last%20ones%2C%20they're%20still%20among%20the%20strongest%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221431%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20graph%20showing%20how%20the%20Intel%20Core%20i7-14700K%20compares%20to%20the%2013700K%20and%2012700K%20in%20benchmark%20tests.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a0149b43bb77284b9c46c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22715%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%2014th%20generation%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20big%20step%20up%20from%20the%2013th%2C%20even%20in%20Intel%E2%80%99s%20own%20benchmarking%20tests.%3Cp%3EIntel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2014th%20generation%20began%20with%20K%2FKF-series%20chips%2C%20which%20are%20generally%20some%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20in%20any%20given%20generation.%20But%20early%202024%20also%20saw%20the%20release%20of%20F-%20and%20T-series%20chips%2C%20which%20cost%20less