0of%20our%20picks%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-laptop%5C%22%3Ebest%20gaming%20laptop%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20laptops%20you%20can%20buy%20now%20with%20Intel%2014th-gen%20CPUs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20for%20laptops%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntel%20Core%20Ultra%3A%20Better%20battery%20life%20and%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221430%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chart%20advertising%20some%20of%20the%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20CPU%E2%80%99s%20features%2C%20including%20faster%20generative%20AI%20performance%20and%20support%20for%20Wi-Fi%207.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a015fedcdb354a9856be1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22715%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20is%20entirely%20separate%20from%20the%20Intel%20Core%2014th%20generation.%3Cp%3EIntel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EReleasing%20alongside%20the%20Intel%20Core%2014th%20generation%20laptop%20chips%20are%20the%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20CPUs%2C%20also%20known%20by%20their%20codename%20%26quot%3BMeteor%20Lake.%26quot%3B%20The%20Core%20Ultra%20processors%20are%20built%20exclusively%20for%20laptops%20and%20tablets%20(although%20a%20version%20for%20all-in-one%20PCs%20is%20on%20its%20way).%20Like%20its%20siblings%2C%20the%20Meteor%20Lake%20line%20includes%20Ultra%205%2C%20Ultra%207%2C%20and%20Ultra%209%20models.%20And%20this%20lineup%20is%20split%20into%20two%20different%20series%3A%20The%20high-end%20H-series%2C%20and%20the%20lower-powered%20U-series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECore%20Ultras%20aren't%20as%20powerful%20as%20other%20premium%20laptop%20CPUs%2C%20but%20they're%20smaller%20and%20much%20more%20power%20efficient%20%E2%80%94%20this%20means%20longer%20battery%20life.%20And%20their%20unique%20construction%20makes%20them%20easier%20and%20quicker%20for%20Intel%20to%20manufacture%2C%20which%20should%20mean%20lower%20prices%20for%20devices%20with%20them%20installed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntel%20Core%20Ultra%20CPUs%20also%20boast%20a%20new%20component%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bneural%20processing%20unit%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BNPU.%26quot%3B%20This%20section%20of%20the%20CPU%20is%20made%20to%20assist%20with%20generative%20AI%20processes%20and%2C%20ideally%2C%20will%20let%20onboard%20AI%20tools%20work%20faster%20without%20having%20to%20rely%20on%20remote%20servers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20sure%20enough%2C%20early%20AI%20process%20testing%20from%20Notebookcheck%20shows%20the%20Ultra-equipped%20Acer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.notebookcheck.net%2FIntel-Meteor-Lake-Analysis-Core-Ultra-7-155H-only-convinces-with-GPU-performance.783320.0.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperforming%20well%20against%20other%20mobile%20CPUs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20taking%20up%20far%20less%20energy%20in%20the%20process.%20This%20means%20that%20Core%20Ultra%20laptops%20will%20work%20best%20for%20consumer-grade%20AI%20use%20in%20apps%20like%20Photoshop%20and%20Stable%20Diffusion%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20put%20heavy%20stress%20on%20laptop%20CPUs%20and%20batteries%20but%20don't%20require%20top-tier%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221431%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20graph%20comparing%20the%20specifications%2C%20including%20core%2Fthread%20count%20and%20clock%20speed%2C%20of%20every%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20CPU%20model.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a0163143bb77284b9c480d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22692%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20line%20is%20split%20into%20two%20series%3A%20H-%20and%20U-series.%3Cp%3EIntel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EExpect%20to%20see%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20chips%20in%20premium%20devices%20that%20prioritize%20