n%20CPUs.%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20laptop%20models%20available%20now%20with%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20a%20new%20Intel%20computer%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20a%20computer%20with%20a%20new%20Intel%20Core%20CPU%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222161%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20logos%20for%20the%20Intel%20Core%20i5%2C%20i7%2C%20and%20i9%20against%20a%20white%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a01686dcdb354a9856be7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221620%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEvery%20CPU%20generation%20comes%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20different%20models.%3Cp%3EIntel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20mainline%2014th-generation%20CPUs%2C%20it%20really%20depends%20on%20the%20price.%20Intel%20has%20set%20its%20MSRP%20at%20the%20same%20price%20as%20the%20older%2013th%20generation%2C%20so%20ideally%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20be%20paying%20that%20much%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20large%20majority%20of%20consumers%2C%20the%20Intel%20Core%2014th%20generation's%20improvements%20are%20marginal%2C%20and%20not%20worth%20spending%20a%20huge%20chunk%20of%20money%20for.%20Only%20professional%20or%20enterprise%20users%20doing%20intense%20work%20in%20bulk%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20editors%20rendering%20multiple%204K%20videos%20each%20day%2C%20or%20finance%20workers%20jumping%20between%20dozens%20of%20massive%20spreadsheets%20%E2%80%94%20will%20appreciate%20the%20small%20performance%20gains.%20But%20many%20of%20those%20same%20enterprise%20users%20would%20probably%20be%20better%20off%20buying%20an%20enterprise-focused%20CPU%20like%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amd.com%2Fen%2Fprocessors%2Fryzen-threadripper-pro%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAMD%20Threadripper%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can't%20afford%20a%20PC%20with%20an%20Intel%2014th-generation%20CPU%2C%20don't%20panic.%20The%20cheaper%2013th-generation%20CPUs%20are%20still%20fantastic%2C%20and%20AMD's%20current%20top-tier%20Ryzen%20processors%20are%20great%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%2C%20most%20consumers%20aren't%20going%20to%20have%20much%20choice%20over%20whether%20they%20buy%20a%20new%20laptop%20with%20one%20or%20not.%20After%20all%2C%20you%20can't%20build%20your%20own%20laptop%20(not%20easily%2C%20at%20least)%2C%20and%20most%20laptop%20companies%20don't%20offer%20many%20customization%20options.%20Companies%20like%20Asus%20are%20actively%20porting%20the%20majority%20of%20their%20Intel-based%20laptops%20over%20to%20the%20Ultra%20lineup%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20a%20bad%20thing.%20Core%20Ultra%20chips%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20higher%20end%2C%20are%20great%20processors%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20users.%20They%20don't%20offer%20much%20of%20a%20performance%20boost%20over%20similarly%20priced%20hardware%2C%20but%20their%20better%20power%20efficiency%20means%20longer%20battery%20life%20and%20lower%20temperatures.%20Besides%2C%20if%20you're%20using%20a%20thin%20laptop%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20expect%20maximum%20performance%20anyway.%20And%20AI%20enthusiasts%20will%20appreciate%20the%20new%20Neural%20Processing%20Unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What's%20on%20the%20horizon%20for%20Intel%20CPUs%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20on%20the%20horizon%20for%20Intel%20CPUs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222295%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chart%20showing%20three%20possible%20new%20CPUs%20that%20Intel%20intends%20to%20release%20in%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a016b543bb77284b9c4880%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221147%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20CES%2C%20Intel%20discussed%20its%20future%20%E2%80%9CArrow%20Lake%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CLunar%20Lake%E2%80%9D%20CPUs.%3Cp%3EIntel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20hype%20that%20Intel%20is%20giving%20its%2014th-generation%20Intel%20Core%20CPUs%2C%20there%20are%20some%20reasons%20to%20suspect%20that%20they%20might%20not%20last%20as%20long%20as%20previous%20generations%20did.%20Case%20in%20point%3A%20At%20CES%202024%2C%20as%20the%2014th%20generation%20HX-series%20and%20Core%20Ultra%20chips%20were%20landing%20on%20store%20shelves%2C%20Intel%20showed%20off%20two%20additional%20new%20processor%20lines.%20Both%20are%20set%20for%20release%20in%20Fall%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20the%20%26quot%3BArrow%20Lake%26quot%3B%20series%2C%20a%20line%20of%20gaming-focused%20chips%20that%20include%20an%20%26quot%3BAI%20accelerator%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20be%20available%20on%20both%20desktops%20and%20laptops.%20It's%20intended%20as%20a%20direct%20successor%20to%20the%20first%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20processors%2C%20and%20will%20likely%20be%20marketed%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BIntel%20Core%20Ultra%202.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%20the%20%26quot%3BLunar%20Lake%26quot%3B%20series%2C%20which%20is%20a%20mobile%20chip%20designed%20for%20%26quot%3Bthin%20and%20light%20PCs.%26quot%3B%20This%20chip%20features%20an%20upgraded%20NPU%20but%20also%20has%20a%20much%20lower%20power%20rating%2C%20meaning%20it'll%20likely%20be%20the%20CPU%20of%20choice%20for%20casual%20AI%20hobbyists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInformation%20about%20Arrow%20and%20Lunar%20Lake%20is%20scarce%2C%20so%20only%20time%20will%20tell%20whether%20they%20end%20up%20replacing%20Raptor%20and%20Meteor%20Lake%20or%20simply%20complementing%20them.%20Either%20way%2C%202024%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20big%20year%20for%20Intel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fintel-14th-generation-core-and-core-ultra-release-date-specs%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22pub