times%20he%20would%20try%20to%20kiss%20me%2C%20but%20I%20told%20him%20that%20wasn't%20okay%20and%20he%20knew%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202015%2C%20Huskins%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fsurvivors-called-girl-case-reflect-life-changing-experience%2Fstory%3Fid%3D77964075%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscovered%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Quinn%20had%20been%20messaging%20Roberts%20about%20getting%20back%20together%2C%20leaving%20her%20devastated.%20Huskins%20was%20uncertain%20about%20whether%20to%20continue%20the%20relationship%20but%20ultimately%20agreed%20to%20get%20together%20at%20Quinn's%20home%20to%20discuss%20their%20future%20on%20March%2022%2C%202015%20%E2%80%94%20the%20night%20before%20she%20was%20kidnapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20harrowing%20ordeal%2C%20Huskins%20recalled%20how%20her%20kidnapper%20(later%20revealed%20to%20be%20Muller)%20told%20her%20that%20Roberts%2C%20who%20had%20previously%20lived%20in%20Quinn's%20home%20and%20looked%20similar%20to%20Huskins%2C%20was%20actually%20the%20intended%20target.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20days%20in%20captivity%2C%20Muller%20drove%20Huskins%20over%20400%20miles%20to%20her%20family%20home%20in%20Huntington%20Beach%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20and%20let%20her%20go.%20Because%20of%20Quinn's%20delay%20in%20initially%20reporting%20Huskins'%20abduction%2C%20and%20after%20learning%20about%20their%20relationship%20troubles%2C%20the%20police%20became%20suspicious%20and%20accused%20the%20couple%20of%20staging%20the%20incident%2C%20comparing%20the%20events%20to%20the%202014%20movie%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-fincher-movies-ranked-worst-best%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BGone%20Girl%2C%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20the%202012%20book%20of%20the%20same%20name%20by%20Gillian%20Flynn.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20David%20Fincher%20film%20sees%20Amy%20Dunne%20(Rosamund%20Pike)%20fake%20her%20own%20kidnappi