20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20failed%20to%20catch%20wind%20of%20or%20prevent%20Hamas-led%20militants%20from%20massacring%20over%201%2C100%20Israelis%20and%20kidnapping%20a%20further%20240.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-military-idf-technology-surveillance-fence-strategy-ground-war%2F%5C%22%3EExperts%20say%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20army%E2%80%99s%20overreliance%20on%20algorithmic%20surveillance%20systems%2C%20drone%20reconnaissance%2C%20and%20AI-powered%20weaponry%20%E2%80%94%20all%20hot%20commodities%20in%20the%20world%20of%20defense%20tech%20%E2%80%94%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20tragic%20and%20unprecedented%20loss%20of%20life.%20Hamas%20was%20able%20to%20take%20the%20majority%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20apparatus%20and%20automated%20weapons%20arsenal%20offline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20the%20events%20of%20October%207%20demonstrate%20an%20inherent%20problem%20in%20the%20promise%20of%20these%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20Neve%20Gordon%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20international%20law%20at%20Queen%20Mary%20University%20of%20London%2C%20told%20%2B972.%20Yet%20defense%20tech%20manufacturers%20could%20never%20admit%20that%20relying%20on%20their%20products%20is%20a%20dead-end%20strategy.%20As%20Gordon%20put%20it%3A%20%E2%80%9CNow%20the%20industry%20has%20a%20vested%20interest%20in%20showing%20that%20the%20failure%20was%20not%20due%20to%20their%20technologies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20forcing%20a%20reckoning%20with%20military%20strategy%2C%20the%20current%20war%20has%20only%20made%20the%20revolving%20door%20between%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20establishment%20and%20its%20private%20defense%20tech%20sector%20spin%20faster.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20a%20large%20resurgence%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20of%20a%20number%20of%20Israeli%20tech%20and%20defense%20start-ups%20using%20the%20events%20of%20October%207%20as%20a%20key%20