mag.com%2Fmass-assassination-factory-israel-calculated-bombing-gaza%2F%5C%22%3Eblasting%20out%20entire%20neighborhoods%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F12%2F21%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-gaza-bomb-investigation.html%5C%22%3E2%2C000-pound%20bombs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20damaging%20or%20destroying%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fgaza-destruction-bombing-israel-aa528542%5C%22%3E70%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20homes%20in%20Gaza.%20Algorithmically%20enhanced%20sniper%20rifles%20have%20done%20little%20to%20deter%20troops%20from%20firing%20at%20civilians%2C%20including%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fthree-hostages-killed-gaza-israeli-soldiers%2F%5C%22%3Ethree%20Israeli%20hostages%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20AI-powered%20targeting%20systems%20have%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67764664%5C%22%3Efailed%20to%20protect%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20lives%20of%20more%20than%208%2C000%20children%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20airstrikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20failures%20suggest%20an%20alternative%20way%20of%20viewing%20the%20events%20of%20October%207%3A%20through%20the%20boom%20and%20bust%20cycle%20of%20financial%20capital.%20High-tech%20weaponry%20offered%20exciting%20solutions%20to%20regional%20insecurity%3B%20enthusiasm%20got%20out%20of%20hand%3B%20and%20the%20bubble%20eventually%20burst.%20As%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20diverting%20resources%20away%20from%20ground%20troops%20and%20pouring%20money%20into%20cutting-edge%20military%20technology%20did%20little%20to%20safeguard%20Israeli%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20investment%20cycle%20has%20a%20short-term%20memory%20problem.%20Three%20months%20into%20a%20war%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Fjan%2F07%2Fisrael-says-gaza-fighting-could-last-a-year-amplifying-fears-of-regional-war%5C%22%3EIsrael%20warns%3C