reserve.%20As%20of%202021%2C%20the%20number%20of%20tigers%20in%20Sariska%20Tiger%20Reserve%20grew%20to%20around%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20many%20had%20attempted%20to%20start%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334903%2Fmudhouse-cottages-homestay-kerala-western-ghats-vacation-marayoor-sandalwood-forest-reserve%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20area%2C%20Luv%20says%20being%20a%20pioneer%20comes%20with%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20area%20was%20remote%2C%20there%20were%20no%20proper%20roads%20built%20and%20no%C2%A0%20electricity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20in%20the%20face%20of%20difficulty%2C%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20natural%20terrain%20and%20its%20potential%20kept%20him%20going.%20After%20five%20years%20of%20work%20on%20the%20land%2C%20in%20October%202015%2C%20Utsav%20Camp%20was%20ready%20to%20open%20its%20arms%20to%20its%20first%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-6_11zon-1705577795.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indigenous%20trees%20like%20neem%20and%20jamun%20fill%20the%20landscape%20of%20Utsav%20Camp%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-6_11zon-1705577795.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-6_11zon-1705577795-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-6_11zon-1705577795-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fsustainable-nature-retreat-6_11zon-1705577795-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20htt