us%3B%20the%20industry%20is%20still%20nascent%2C%20and%20people%20are%20only%20now%20beginning%20to%20open%20up.%20Back%20in%202013%2C%20when%20I%20started%20my%20research%2C%20there%20were%20no%20avenues%20available.%20Institutes%20dedicated%20to%20this%20cause%20were%20scarce%2C%20and%20the%20technology%20to%20do%20simple%20things%20like%20making%20uttapam%20from%20jowar%20was%20not%20readily%20accessible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CTimes%20have%20changed%20significantly%20since%20then.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%20dedicated%20institutes%20for%20research%2C%20and%20more%20individuals%20are%20investing%20in%20millet-based%20startups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20year%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F305138%2Fmasterchef-india-contestant-whips-up-gluten-free-desserts-in-her-house-of-millets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einitiative%20for%20millets%20%3C%2Fa%3Elast%20year%20has%20undoubtedly%20made%20a%20positive%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20believe%20it%E2%80%99s%20still%20in%20the%20awareness%20stage%20rather%20than%20a%20point%20where%20a%20habit%20has%20been%20fully%20formed.%20People%20are%20trying%2C%20and%20experimenting%2C%20but%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20become%20a%20daily%20habit%20like%20eating%20rice%20or%20chapati.%20That%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20will%20take%20some%20more%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20products%20by%20Health%20Sutra%20are%20currently%20available%20in%20close%20to%203%2C000%20supermarkets%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana.%20They%20also%20ship%20them%20country-wide%20via%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-8-1