d%20of%20access%20they%20should%20actually%20not%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMinimise%20the%20use%20of%20Gmail%20everywhere%20because%20if%20your%20phone%20is%20hacked%2C%20the%20hacker%20gets%20access%20to%20your%20phone%20and%20contacts%20because%20Gmail%20is%20linked%20to%20your%20contacts%20and%20gallery.%20Also%2C%20you%20must%20mask%20the%20camera%20on%20your%20laptop%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Change%20your%20privacy%20settings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20of%20cybercrime%2C%20firstly%20your%20WhatsApp%20is%20compromised.%20So%2C%20I%20suggest%20you%20ensure%20end-to-end%20encryption%20on%20WhatsApp.%20Also%2C%20many%20people%20do%20not%20know%20that%20they%20can%20choose%20%E2%80%98silence%20unknown%20callers%E2%80%99%20and%20protect%20their%20IP%20addresses%20by%20changing%20privacy%20settings.%20You%20must%20enable%20it%20to%20secure%20yourself%20from%20cybercriminals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Reboot%20your%20phone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179257%2Fmumbai-couple-troll-police-cyberbullying-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evictim%20of%20cybercrime%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20you%20should%20first%20deactivate%20your%20WhatsApp%20account%20immediately%20and%20remove%20photos%20from%20the%20gallery.%20Thereafter%2C%20you%20must%20reboot%20your%20phone.%20This%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20hacker%20loses%20access%20to%20your%20data%20and%20all%20the%20apps%20are%20closed%20automatically%2C%E2%80%9D%20suggests%20Murthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20police%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20our%20work%2C%20we%20can%20trace%20the%20location%20but%20not%20the%20person.%20It%20is%20illegal.%20It%20is%20the%20police%20whom%20one%20should%20seek%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20of%20harassment%20or%20defamation%20on%20social%20media%20verticals%20like%20Instagram%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20Facebook%2C%20police%20write%20to%20their%20parent%20company%20Meta%20and%20report%20the%20profile.%20They%20will%20monitor%20their%20cookies%2C%20browsing%20history%2C%20and%20messages.%20So%2C%20not%20only%20will%20they%20find%20their%20location%20using%20the%20IP%20address%20but%20also%20identify%20the%20criminal.%20So%2C%20the%20right%20way%20is%20to%20approach%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Register%20your%20complaint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurthy%20advises%20victims%20to%20report%20cyber%20complaints%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcybercrime.gov.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybercrime.gov.in%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20portal%20has%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20financial%20frauds%20and%20cybercrime%20related%20to%20women%20and%20children.%20It%20also%20allows%20victims%20to%20report%20a%20complaint%20anonymously%20as%20well.%20Here%2C%20you%20do%20not%20need%20to%20visit%20the%20police%20station%20every%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Radha%20Krishna%20Murthy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705502267000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fcybercrime-seurity-2-1705499767.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D338444%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Radha%20Krishna%20Murthy%2C%20a%20cybercrime%20survivor%2C%20founded%20'Global%20Security%20Council'%20after%20facing%20deep%20fake%20abuse%20and%20loan%20scam.%20He%20shares%20five%20steps%20for%20cybercrime%20victims%20to%20protect%20themselves.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gu